### Graduate Program Research API Calls
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@jwtToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Research Programs Based on Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Research and find graduate programs that match my background and interests"
}

